  <h2>Critical Resources</h2>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Each race has a set of resources that provide special
  bonuses to its colonies. These bonuses include things like increasing
  happiness or population growth rate, making newly recruited troops strong=
er,
  or providing a development bonus for the colony.</p>
  <h2>Race Victory Conditions</h2>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Each alien race has unique victory conditions that m=
atch
  the race&#8217;s personality. These conditions help focus the game-play in
  the areas that the race specializes in.</p>
